          %h2.text-center#when When is it?
          %p A date has yet to be set with finality, but we're probably going to shoot for some Saturday in May or June, 2013. If this first go-round is a success, we may make this a regular thing, but we'll cross that bridge when we get there. Check back here soon for the final date!
