      .row
        .span10.offset1
          %h2.text-center#want Want to help?
          %p If you're on the more experienced side of things and would be interested in so doing, we still need a volunteer to act as one more Wandering Tutor! This has little requirement, save that you preclude yourself from participating in a team directly, and make yourself available to help out anyone who might need it to the best of your ability. If interested, please contact the organizers (see below)!
          %hr
